<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195662>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Alpheus baccheti n. sp., holotype, male (CL 13.5 mm) from Makemo, Tuamotu Islands (FLMNH UF Arthropoda 18556): a, frontal region, dorsal; b, same, lateral; c, telson, dorsal; d, same, detail of posterolateral spiniform setae; e, lateral antennular flagellum, lateral; f, tooth on mesioventral carina of first segment of antennular peduncle, lateral; g, third maxilliped, lateral; h, second pleopod, detail of appendices masculina and interna; i, uropod, lateral; j, same, detail of row of spiniform setae on distal margin of endopod." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195662/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195663>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Alpheus baccheti n. sp., holotype, male (CL 13.5 mm) from Makemo, Tuamotu Islands (FLMNH UF Arthropoda 18556), major cheliped: a, general view, lateral; b, same, mesial; c, fingers opened, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195663/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195664>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Alpheus baccheti n. sp., holotype, male (CL 13.5 mm) from Makemo, Tuamotu Islands (FLMNH UF Arthropoda 18556), minor cheliped: a, general view, lateral; b, same, detail of distal portion of merus and carpus, mesial; c, chela, lateral; d, same, mesial." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195664/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195665>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Alpheus baccheti n. sp., holotype, male (CL 13.5 mm) from Makemo, Tuamotu Islands (FLMNH UF Arthropoda 18556): a, second pereiopod, lateral; b, third pereiopod, lateral; c, same, detail of distal propodus and dactylus; d, fifth pereiopod, lateral; e, same, propodus and dactylus, mesial." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195665/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195666>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Alpheus baccheti n. sp., holotype, male (CL 13.5 mm) from Makemo, Tuamotu Islands (FLMNH UF Arthropoda 18556): a, shrimp shortly after capture; b, shrimp in situ. Photographs by Philippe Bacchet." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195666/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

